msgid "Justin built workflows for notifications across the team, alerting the right people in Teams when a prospect becomes a lead or when project milestones are reached. Forms in Twenty let the business development team log activity without leaving the tool. The impact is real for the organization. The tool has been adaptable from opportunity-level work at a client to executive-level decisions."
